---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team - Neon Injector"
  description="Meet Agung, Andrian, and Gura, the talented team behind Neon Injector, dedicated to enhancing your Mobile Legends experience with innovative skin injection solutions."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-6 text-center">Our Team</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">At Neon Injector, our small but passionate team drives innovation in Mobile Legends skin customization. Led by our visionary CEO, Agung, we combine technical expertise with a love for gaming to deliver a seamless, safe, and user-friendly experience. Get to know the brilliant minds behind Neon Injector.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- CEO Section -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-neon-purple-dark max-w-md mx-auto text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/agung-dev.webp" alt="CEO & Developer Agung" class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Agung</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">CEO & Lead Developer</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">With 12+ years of Android development expertise, Agung founded Neon Injector to empower Mobile Legends players with cutting-edge skin customization. He leads the technical vision, ensuring compatibility and performance across all devices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <!-- Team Members Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-neon-purple-dark text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/andrian-dev.webp" alt="Developer Andrian" class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Andrian</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">Developer</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Andrian optimizes Neon Injector’s core performance, focusing on fast and secure skin injection processes to ensure a smooth experience across diverse Android devices.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-neon-purple-dark text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/gura-dev.webp" alt="Developer Gura" class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Gura</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">Developer</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gura specializes in expanding our skin library and rigorously testing compatibility with Mobile Legends updates, delivering a bug-free experience for all users.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-4">Our Commitment to Excellence</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Under Agung’s leadership, our team is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of Mobile Legends customization. We continuously update Neon Injector to support new skins, enhance performance, and incorporate community feedback. Join our vibrant community on <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord</a> or stay updated via our <a href="/blog" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Blog</a>.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-4 mt-8">Join Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Passionate about gaming and technology? We’re always seeking talented developers and designers to join our team. Reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact</a> page to explore opportunities.</p>
          <img src="/images/team-collaboration.webp" alt="Team Collaboration" class="w-full rounded-lg mt-8" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>